2
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,040
Miss Zhou refuses to leave.

3
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,639
She insists on seeing you.

4
00:00:27,639 --> 00:00:29,279
Got it.

5
00:00:30,050 --> 00:00:39,070


6
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:43,499
Have a seat.

7
00:00:50,999 --> 00:00:54,719
Hello, Miss Jiang. I'm Zhou Xiao Qing.

8
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:56,940
Sorry to intrude today.

9
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,079
It's fine.

10
00:00:59,079 --> 00:01:02,179
Miss Zhou, how can I help you?

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:11,060
Miss Jiang, I know you and Dong Yang are engaged,
but he doesn't love you.

12
00:01:11,060 --> 00:01:12,860
He never has.

13
00:01:12,860 --> 00:01:17,179
If he did,
he wouldn't have been with me for so long.

14
00:01:17,179 --> 00:01:20,020
Miss Jiang, I just don't get it.

15
00:01:20,020 --> 00:01:22,530
Why would someone as wealthy as you

16
00:01:22,530 --> 00:01:26,600
choose to be with a man who doesn't love you?

17
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:32,040
Miss Jiang, please, let him be with me.

18
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:34,700
Miss Zhou, please get up.

19
00:01:43,099 --> 00:01:47,220
Miss Zhou, what's your definition of wealth?

20
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:54,920
Money is money only within a certain range.

21
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:58,760
Miss Jiang, I don't understand what you mean.

22
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:04,500
Once it goes beyond that range,
it's no longer just money.

23
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:06,439
It's a person's entire life at stake.

24
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:09,380
No one would give up their own life willingly.

25
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:13,179
I won't, and Shen Dong Yang
certainly won't either.

26
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:17,639
Miss Zhou, please leave.

27
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:25,100
I always do everything he says.

28
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:34,499
I wear whatever he tells me to wear,
and speak the way he likes.

29
00:02:35,899 --> 00:02:38,619
Am I not doing a good job of imitating her?

30
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:47,079
Miss Zhou, what did you mean by that?

31
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,100
Who are you imitating?

32
00:02:50,899 --> 00:02:53,140
I can't break up with him.

33
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:55,239
He cares about me.

34
00:02:55,239 --> 00:02:58,359
- I must head back now and behave myself.
- Ke Rui,

35
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:01,860
see Miss Zhou out.

36
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:04,020
Let's go, Miss Zhou.

37
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:12,760
 ♫ When can I Stop panicking ♫ 

38
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:19,079
What rouge and perfume
has Miss Jiang been using lately?

39
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,760
I can't tell you.

40
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:24,190
Miss Zhou, since you've chosen to be a mistress,

41
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:26,420
learn not to overstep your boundaries.

42
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,980
Take care.

43
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:33,639
 ♫ Why am I still greedy? ♫ 

44
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,580
Miss, please.

45
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:39,580
 ♫ When I take off the evening dress naked ♫ 

46
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:43,400
 ♫ But my eyes still look dull ♫ 

47
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:49,559
 Up until now, Zhou Xiao Qing
still doesn't understand what she did wrong 

48
00:03:49,559 --> 00:03:53,139
 or why Shen Dong Yang suddenly turned on her. 

49
