 That morning, 

50
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,440
 she and Shen Dong Yang had breakfast together for the first time in ages, 

51
00:03:57,440 --> 00:04:01,280
 so sweet it felt like they were
just any ordinary couple. 

52
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:06,160
 ♫ I might as well forget my wandering days ♫ 

53
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:11,480
Dong Yang, how often do you see your fiancée
in a year?

54
00:04:12,359 --> 00:04:14,380
Not as much as I see you.

55
00:04:15,359 --> 00:04:17,979
What does she look like?

56
