58
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,600
Is she as pretty as me?

59
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,600
Is she ugly?

60
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,220
Is that why she never shows her face?

61
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:37,660
 ♫ When I take off the evening dress naked ♫ 

62
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:42,180
 ♫ But my eyes still look dull ♫ 

63
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:45,020
Why aren't you saying anything?

64
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:47,859
