because she won't let you touch her?

66
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:58,859
Zhou Xiao Qing, stop being such a lunatic.

67
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:02,219
Shen Dong Yang, stop right there!

68
00:05:02,219 --> 00:05:05,979
If you walk out that door today,
don't ever come back to me.

69
00:05:05,979 --> 00:05:09,200
There are plenty of rich, powerful men chasing after me,

70
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,980
