75
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,679
What is it?

76
00:05:42,679 --> 00:05:46,559
Are you going to lecture me again, Mr. Fu?

77
00:05:47,559 --> 00:05:50,840
So, you're marrying
Shen Dong Yang no matter what, right?

78
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,419
Is there something wrong with that?

79
00:05:52,419 --> 00:05:55,270
Even if he's been hurting you,

80
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:58,239
fooling around with women, causing scandals,

81
00:05:58,239 --> 00:06:01,559
and getting another woman to dress up like you?

82
00:06:01,559 --> 00:06:03,519
Don't you find that...

83
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,299
What?

84
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,879
Disgusting?

85
00:06:13,239 --> 00:06:17,559
Mr. Fu, you really are quite naive.

86
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,090
The purer someone is,

87
00:06:22,980 --> 00:06:28,620
the more it makes people want to destroy them.

88
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,199
Do you like them?

89
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:53,459
Do you know what I do, looking at these photos,
when I stay late at the office?

90
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:09,339
 ♫ You were a storm, scattering ♫ 

91
00:07:09,339 --> 00:07:12,020
You... How could you...

92
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:14,200
Why not?

93
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:17,120
 ♫ The wreckage,
what do you want me to do with it? ♫ 

94
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:22,300
 ♫ I pick it up,
then throw it back into my memories ♫ 

95
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:25,340
 ♫ I hide in this fragile room ♫ 

96
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:29,480
 ♫ Shedding tears,
blaming you for your sweet words ♫ 

97
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:32,520
 ♫ What gave you the strength to move on from us? ♫ 

98
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:38,320
 ♫ Leaving silently without a trace ♫ 

99
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:41,180
 ♫ You were a ruthless storm ♫ 

100
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:46,180
 ♫ Drowning my love, offering no respite ♫ 

101
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:49,180
 ♫ I'm in my thin clothes, curled up ♫ 

102
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:54,280
 ♫ In the silence you left me, without a word ♫ 

103
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:57,220
 ♫ How am I supposed to face this endgame ♫ 

104
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:02,080
 ♫ Without you by my side? ♫ 

105
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,120
 ♫ Your warmth and sweetness ♫ 

106
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:06,580
 ♫ Are etched in my mind ♫ 

107
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:09,760
 ♫ How am I supposed to forget? ♫ 

108
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,040
 

109
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:29,000
 

110
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,719
- Boss.
- Ying Xian.

111
00:08:42,719 --> 00:08:47,299
- Granduncle.
- Let me get down on my knees first.

112
00:08:47,299 --> 00:08:48,920
Granduncle!

113
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:56,160
- Let's talk over there.
- Alright.

114
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,479
Have a seat.

115
00:09:07,457 --> 00:09:09,097
Be careful.

116
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:16,419
Isn't this all such a headache?

117
00:09:16,419 --> 00:09:18,160
I really don't know...

118
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:57,500
 

119
