Ke Rui told me you went out,
but I knew I'd find you here.

129
00:11:13,899 --> 00:11:17,199
As expected, we are in tune with each other.

130
00:11:17,199 --> 00:11:20,240
You seem eager to see me.
Let's talk upstairs.

131
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,320
I came to apologize,

132
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:26,500
and I hope you can spare some time to have dinner with me.

133
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:29,420
It would be my honor.

134
00:11:30,939 --> 00:11:36,120
In that case, Mr. Fu,
please let me take over from here.

135
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:40,939
Let us, as an engaged couple,
have some time alone.

136
00:11:43,037 --> 00:11:46,397
Mr. Fu, you can leave early today.

137
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:13,160
 

138
00:12:29,839 --> 00:12:32,700
I only ordered this today.

139
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:35,620
- You don't mind, do you?
- Of course not.

140
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:54,200
Zhou Xiao Qing came to see you a few days ago,
right?

141
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,280
Yes.

142
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:59,199
 Is Shen Dong Yang mad? 

143
00:12:59,199 --> 00:13:01,120
 Is he unhappy with how I reacted? 

144
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,779
 Why? 

145
00:13:02,779 --> 00:13:04,220
This is your personal matter.

146
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:10,660
I shouldn't interfere,
but I do think you could've handled it better.

147
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:15,160
Well... You haven't changed at all,
Jiang Ying Xian.

148
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:19,959
But she told me everything
you two talked about.

149
00:13:19,959 --> 00:13:21,479
Oh, did she?

150
00:13:21,479 --> 00:13:23,280
 I see. 

151
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:27,079
 As his fiancée,
when his mistress showed up at my door, 

152
00:13:27,079 --> 00:13:29,920
 I was supposed to be angry, upset, 

153
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:33,579
 or at least throw out a few sarcastic remarks, 

154
00:13:33,579 --> 00:13:35,939
 even though that would only annoy him. 

155
00:13:35,939 --> 00:13:40,220
 The point is, in his eyes,
there can only be people who are rejected by him, 

156
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:42,500
 not the other way around. 

157
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:52,319
Did you tell her
your life is on the line because of me?

158
00:13:52,319 --> 00:13:54,120
Yes.

159
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:56,100
Isn't that true?

160
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:58,340
Good. Straightforward as always.

161
00:13:58,340 --> 00:14:03,039
It suits our relationship,
which is based on mutual benefits.

162
00:14:03,039 --> 00:14:06,899
There are ways to handle a relationship
built on interests,

163
00:14:06,899 --> 00:14:11,280
and there are ways to handle one based on love.

164
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:13,360
Ying Xian...

165
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,820
how do you want to handle ours?

166
00:14:18,439 --> 00:14:21,430
 If I can't fall in love with Shen Dong Yang, then 

167
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:24,850
 I'll have no choice but to stick to the former. 

168
00:14:25,439 --> 00:14:29,959
 I hope my self-punishment will be enough
to make him drop the topic. 

169
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:34,340
 ♫ I don't have the courage
to face the scars of the past ♫ 

170
00:14:34,340 --> 00:14:36,580
 ♫ After all this time, I'm still not over her ♫ 

171
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:37,940
 ♫ I ask myself, am I at peace? ♫ 

172
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:40,240
 ♫ Can I let go? Do I regret it? ♫ 

173
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:43,080
 ♫ But time can never turn back ♫ 

174
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:48,480
 ♫ I can only carry these memories
and meet her in my dreams ♫ 

175
00:15:01,660 --> 00:15:04,560
 ♫ Imagination and reality are always at odds ♫ 

176
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:08,760
 ♫ Plans can never keep up with changes ♫ 

177
00:15:08,760 --> 00:15:12,320
 ♫ There's nothing we can do about it ♫ 

178
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:15,860
 ♫ We tell the ones we love
that we've never loved them ♫ 

179
00:15:15,860 --> 00:15:17,520
 ♫ We act clueless
in front of those we don't love ♫ 

180
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,820
 ♫ Listening to those who don't love us ♫ 

