191
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,100
Enough, Jiang Ying Xian.

192
00:16:06,439 --> 00:16:08,260
Stop drinking.

193
00:16:09,479 --> 00:16:12,579
Have you had your fill, Mr. Shen?

194
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,340
I brought this from Haicheng.

195
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:21,260
You haven't eaten anything today.

196
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:23,380
Take it home. Have it as a late-night snack.

197
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:32,179
You could've smoothed things over
with a few sweet words,

198
00:16:32,179 --> 00:16:35,990
but no, you chose to drink

199
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:38,590
and throw soft jabs at me.

200
00:16:38,599 --> 00:16:41,500
What a troublesome personality.

201
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:44,179
Thank you for the gift.

202
00:16:44,179 --> 00:16:46,160
Let me walk you home.

203
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,640
It's okay.

204
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:51,380
Ke Rui will take me back.

205
00:17:10,360 --> 00:17:16,420
Zhou Xiao Qing
really doesn't deserve any sympathy.

206
00:17:16,420 --> 00:17:19,660
The moment she saw him,
she sold me out completely.

207
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:23,600
Her tears are genuine,
but her manipulations are real too.

208
00:17:26,399 --> 00:17:29,220
Shen Dong Yang and I are no different.

209
00:17:29,220 --> 00:17:34,760
We look decent on the outside,
but inside, we're both falling apart.

210
00:17:35,940 --> 00:17:39,380
I'm worse than Shen Dong Yang,

211
00:17:39,380 --> 00:17:41,900
but no one knows.

212
00:17:45,339 --> 00:17:48,859
No, there's one person who knows.

213
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,919
Hi.

214
00:17:53,919 --> 00:17:56,959
You look like the person I was talking about.

215
00:18:04,299 --> 00:18:06,020
Get on.

216
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:09,740
Why? Who do you think you are?

217
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:11,299
I'm Fu Cheng.

218
00:18:11,299 --> 00:18:14,090
Jiang Ying Xian, get on.

219
